trans-unit.source: Specifies whether a calendar is solar-based, lunar-based, or lunisolar-based.
trans-unit.target: Angir om en kalender er sol-baserte, månekalender kodebasert eller lunisolar basert på.

trans-unit.source: A date calculation for a particular calendar depends on whether the calendar is solar-based, lunar-based, or lunisolar-based.
trans-unit.target: En beregning for en bestemt kalender avhenger om kalenderen sol basert, månekalender kodebasert eller lunisolar-basert.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>, <xref:System.Globalization.JapaneseCalendar>, and <xref:System.Globalization.JulianCalendar> classes are solar-based, the <xref:System.Globalization.HijriCalendar> and <xref:System.Globalization.UmAlQuraCalendar> classes are lunar-based,.and the <xref:System.Globalization.HebrewCalendar> and <xref:System.Globalization.JapaneseLunisolarCalendar> classes are lunisolar-based, thus using solar calculations for the year and lunar calculations for the month and day.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>, <xref:System.Globalization.JapaneseCalendar>, og <xref:System.Globalization.JulianCalendar>klasser er sol-baserte, den <xref:System.Globalization.HijriCalendar>og <xref:System.Globalization.UmAlQuraCalendar>klasser er månekalender-baserte, og den <xref:System.Globalization.HebrewCalendar>og <xref:System.Globalization.JapaneseLunisolarCalendar>klasser er lunisolar-baserte, derfor ved hjelp av sol beregninger år og månekalender beregninger for måneden og dagen.</xref:System.Globalization.JapaneseLunisolarCalendar> </xref:System.Globalization.HebrewCalendar> </xref:System.Globalization.UmAlQuraCalendar> </xref:System.Globalization.HijriCalendar> </xref:System.Globalization.JulianCalendar> </xref:System.Globalization.JapaneseCalendar> </xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>

trans-unit.source: A CalendarAlgorithmType value, which is returned by a calendar member such as the <xref:System.Globalization.Calendar.AlgorithmType%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, specifies the foundation for a particular calendar.
trans-unit.target: En CalendarAlgorithmType-verdi som er returnert av medlem kalenderen som den <xref:System.Globalization.Calendar.AlgorithmType%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen angir grunnlag for en bestemt kalender.</xref:System.Globalization.Calendar.AlgorithmType%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
